2. Review classification tiers against the organisation's data landscape
3. Map existing data assets to the classification tiers
4. Train staff on classification procedures and AI-specific rules
5. Implement technical controls to enforce classification (labelling, access controls)
6. Distribute the policy with mandatory acknowledgement
{% elif "incident" in action.name | lower %}
