2. Customise the plan with organisation-specific contacts and procedures
3. Establish the incident response team and assign roles
4. Communicate the plan to all staff
5. Schedule the first tabletop exercise within 90 days
6. Test notification procedures with a dry run
{% elif "governance contact" in action.name | lower %}
1. Identify a suitable individual with authority over AI usage
2. Document their responsibilities in a formal role description
3. Communicate the appointment organisation-wide
4. Update all AI governance documents with their contact details
